cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.DS

This paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category as it discusses the evaluation of systems doing deterministic planning. It may also belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category as it introduces a new language called PDDL2.2. Additionally, it could be classified under Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) as it deals with formal language and reasoning. Software Engineering (cs.SE) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses the organization and results of a competition event. Finally, Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) could be a relevant sub-category as the paper may discuss the efficiency and performance of the competing systems.
